{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And actually I wanted to go and study somewhere out of Poland to learn some practical things like, in my mind, was then dye works, or [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fur, dying fur, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] learning to make bricks-- something, a speciality with which I could travel around the world, and did not have borders.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "At the once you change the border, you couldn't use what you knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I couldn't do it, because my parents couldn't afford, in those days already, to pay for my [INTERPOSING VOICES].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I matriculated in 1931.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One, two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I decided-- I always was very interested in law, so I decided to study law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I studied law at the Krakow and the Jagiellonian University, which was oldest university in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did as well political science.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was the law faculty, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The difficulties were mainly in medical faculty, veterinary science, and engineering.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In medical faculty exists the so-called numerous classes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Jews formed about 10% of the total population in Poland, 10% of the seats were available for them at the university.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the competition for admission to the university was not against the Poles, or with the Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was one Jew against the other Jew, because there were so many Jewish entries, and it was depending which Jew, who got it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In law was no-- at the university level-- was not restriction, because it was no practical restriction how many people attended.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't require any special facilities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to learn the subject, and pass the exams, take part eventually in seminaries, and this was all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the restrictions were later.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
